   Mayor Anthony A. Williams Kicks Off 2002 Tax Filing Season
   The District is the first US city to offer online tax services for
   residents and businesses. Full Text

   Office of Tax and Revenue Offers Online Application for New Business
   Registration
   New businesses to the District can now complete and submit the Combined
   Business Tax Registration Application (form FR-500) online. Full Text

   District Makes Last Effort To Confirm Real Property Tax Relief
   Eligibility
   The OTR has publicized on the Internet thousands of real properties
   whose owners have not confirmed their eligibility for Homestead and
   Senior Citizen tax relief. Full Text
